org.barghos.core.api.tuple

Interface ITup2fR

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITup2R, ITupfR, ITupR
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PTup2f, Tup2f

    public interface ITup2fR
extends ITupfR, ITup2R
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 2-dimensional float tuple.
